Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The most crucial moment in life is during decision making.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But also instilled \Nnumerous lessons on how to live.{unsure, lit is "for the sake of living, precepts, numerous left behind"}
